OL,3,CSouth Scotland MSP Colin Smyth charged
OL,4,Cwith possession of indecent images
OL,6,FSouth Scotland MSP Colin Smyth has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with possession of
OL,8,Findecent images.
OL,10,FITV Border News has learned that
OL,11,FSmyth, who has represented the region
OL,12,Fsince 2016, has been "administratively
OL,13,Fsuspended" by Labour while the case
OL,14,Fprogresses.
OL,16,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"On Tuesday, 5 August, 2025, officers
OL,18,Fexecuted a warrant at a property on
OL,19,FMarchfield Avenue, Dumfries.
