OL,3,CSouth Scotland MSP Colin Smyth charged
OL,4,Cwith possession of indecent images
OL,6,F"A 52-year-old man was arrested and
OL,7,Fcharged in connection with possession
OL,8,Fof indecent images. He is due to
OL,9,Fappear at Dumfries Sheriff Court at a
OL,10,Flater date."
OL,12,FSmyth has been removed from the list
OL,13,Fof Labour MSPs on the party's website
OL,14,Fand is now listed as an independent on
OL,15,Fthe Scottish parliament's website.
OL,17,FHe was Scottish Labour's general
OL,18,Fsecretary for just over a year,
OL,19,Fstepping down in 2012, and has held a
OL,20,Fnumber of frontbench roles since being
OL,21,Felected to Holyrood.
