OL,6,FA Labour Party spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,Fwhip has been removed from Colin Smyth
OL,8,FMSP, pending an investigation. We
OL,9,Fcannot comment further on this matter
OL,10,Fwhile the investigation is ongoing."
OL,12,FIt is understood that he was suspended
OL,13,Fand the whip was removed once the
OL,14,Fparty became aware of the
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,FSmyth declined to comment when
OL,18,Fcontacted by ITV Border.
